  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Introduction</h2><br><i>FlippedDream</i> is a physically-based, 3D-platformer and maze-exploring game, developed by Unreal Engine 4.<br><br>You will get into 14 different mazes, trying to find the exit through your exploration.<br><br>At the same time, you can change the direction of the global gravity to go into different channels or avoid obstacles. <br><br><strong>When the gravity is rotating, your camera is rotating as well, causing the loss of your sense of directions. </strong><br><br>And this would be your biggest challenge during the gameplay.<br><br><i>FlippedDream</i> is my graduation project, developed on my own, for the first time. It is not perfect indeed, but hopes to become a part of your memories of video games.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Control</h2><br>A/D: Move left/right.<br><br>Space: Jump.<br><br>Q/E：Rotate the global gravity clockwise/counter clockwise, 90 degrees for each time. You can not change it again until it finishes doing so. <br><br>Esc: Pause;<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Levels</h2><br>The game consists of 5 chapters and 14 levels. You will be faced of multiple obstacles too. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/f95e273ffb95a7c2ce55cb5795eb05c9.avif?t=1768874778\" width=616 height=353 /></span><br><br>1. Simple gravity item<br><br>Some items' gravity directions would also change as the global gravity changes, but some would not.  They have their unique gravity. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/8fa7405d0ec3d929d3ae853cc4517308.poster.avif?t=1768874778\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/8fa7405d0ec3d929d3ae853cc4517308.webm?t=1768874778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/8fa7405d0ec3d929d3ae853cc4517308.mp4?t=1768874778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>2. Single pendulum<br><br>Single pendulum is an anchor, connected to a \"simple gravity item\" by a cable.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/70390ae38c7e78508bab8d93b4d91b4b.poster.avif?t=1768874778\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/70390ae38c7e78508bab8d93b4d91b4b.webm?t=1768874778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/70390ae38c7e78508bab8d93b4d91b4b.mp4?t=1768874778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>3. Gravity converter<br><br>In charpter 3, the player would not be allowed to change gravity at any time, you can only change it when touching the \"gravity converter\".<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/6b953ca153c4663343456681039e8590.poster.avif?t=1768874778\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/6b953ca153c4663343456681039e8590.webm?t=1768874778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/6b953ca153c4663343456681039e8590.mp4?t=1768874778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>4. The fan<br><br>The big fan would be continuesly rotating slowly, blocking the items when contacting them. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/a021a86d0786d52c34fb164e920f8095.poster.avif?t=1768874778\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/a021a86d0786d52c34fb164e920f8095.webm?t=1768874778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/a021a86d0786d52c34fb164e920f8095.mp4?t=1768874778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>5. Diseased cells<br><br>Diseased cells and harmful to healthy ones. When a health cell contacts a diseased one, it would get illed and die. So make sure to avoid them in any case. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/dd0c4f88efbd8b7af1bc52928a8644ef.poster.avif?t=1768874778\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/dd0c4f88efbd8b7af1bc52928a8644ef.webm?t=1768874778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/dd0c4f88efbd8b7af1bc52928a8644ef.mp4?t=1768874778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Additional notes</h2><br>1. No solution<br><br>If an obstacle is stucked in a channel especially which would lead to the exit, you could consider loading the last check point. This would reload the whole level. <br><br>2. Adjusting resolution in fullscreen mode causes the app to flicker or stutter<br><br>Maybe it is because you have installed NVIDIA Game Ready Driver 461.09 or newer. You could find solutions in NVIDIA SUPPORT.",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Introduction</h2><br><i>FlippedDream</i> is a physically-based, 3D-platformer and maze-exploring game, developed by Unreal Engine 4.<br><br>You will get into 14 different mazes, trying to find the exit through your exploration.<br><br>At the same time, you can change the direction of the global gravity to go into different channels or avoid obstacles. <br><br><strong>When the gravity is rotating, your camera is rotating as well, causing the loss of your sense of directions. </strong><br><br>And this would be your biggest challenge during the gameplay.<br><br><i>FlippedDream</i> is my graduation project, developed on my own, for the first time. It is not perfect indeed, but hopes to become a part of your memories of video games.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Control</h2><br>A/D: Move left/right.<br><br>Space: Jump.<br><br>Q/E：Rotate the global gravity clockwise/counter clockwise, 90 degrees for each time. You can not change it again until it finishes doing so. <br><br>Esc: Pause;<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Levels</h2><br>The game consists of 5 chapters and 14 levels. You will be faced of multiple obstacles too. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/f95e273ffb95a7c2ce55cb5795eb05c9.avif?t=1768874778\" width=616 height=353 /></span><br><br>1. Simple gravity item<br><br>Some items' gravity directions would also change as the global gravity changes, but some would not.  They have their unique gravity. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/8fa7405d0ec3d929d3ae853cc4517308.poster.avif?t=1768874778\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/8fa7405d0ec3d929d3ae853cc4517308.webm?t=1768874778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/8fa7405d0ec3d929d3ae853cc4517308.mp4?t=1768874778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>2. Single pendulum<br><br>Single pendulum is an anchor, connected to a \"simple gravity item\" by a cable.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/70390ae38c7e78508bab8d93b4d91b4b.poster.avif?t=1768874778\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/70390ae38c7e78508bab8d93b4d91b4b.webm?t=1768874778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/70390ae38c7e78508bab8d93b4d91b4b.mp4?t=1768874778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>3. Gravity converter<br><br>In charpter 3, the player would not be allowed to change gravity at any time, you can only change it when touching the \"gravity converter\".<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/6b953ca153c4663343456681039e8590.poster.avif?t=1768874778\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/6b953ca153c4663343456681039e8590.webm?t=1768874778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/6b953ca153c4663343456681039e8590.mp4?t=1768874778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>4. The fan<br><br>The big fan would be continuesly rotating slowly, blocking the items when contacting them. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/a021a86d0786d52c34fb164e920f8095.poster.avif?t=1768874778\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/a021a86d0786d52c34fb164e920f8095.webm?t=1768874778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/a021a86d0786d52c34fb164e920f8095.mp4?t=1768874778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>5. Diseased cells<br><br>Diseased cells and harmful to healthy ones. When a health cell contacts a diseased one, it would get illed and die. So make sure to avoid them in any case. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/dd0c4f88efbd8b7af1bc52928a8644ef.poster.avif?t=1768874778\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/dd0c4f88efbd8b7af1bc52928a8644ef.webm?t=1768874778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2430190/extras/dd0c4f88efbd8b7af1bc52928a8644ef.mp4?t=1768874778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Additional notes</h2><br>1. No solution<br><br>If an obstacle is stucked in a channel especially which would lead to the exit, you could consider loading the last check point. This would reload the whole level. <br><br>2. Adjusting resolution in fullscreen mode causes the app to flicker or stutter<br><br>Maybe it is because you have installed NVIDIA Game Ready Driver 461.09 or newer. You could find solutions in NVIDIA SUPPORT.",
